,Recommended,214170,4374417,"Posted: 22 May, 2013",all,MeaslyTripod,"A single-player fantasy RPG with top-down view, the 1st title of Divinity series by Belgian developer Larian Studios. Player can make their characters learn any skill regardless of their initial class. It's up to player to when & where to go, what to do. Sadly the latter 1/3 part is somehow tedious because player's character becomes too strong or enemies too weak, but overall quality is high, especially its graphics and music are impressive. With plenty of sub-quests, at least 40 to 60 hours playing is guaranteed. Getting ""Divinity Anthology"" which includes 3 titles of the series (this game and its spin-off ""Beyond Divinity"" and ultimate edition of sequel ""Divinity 2 Developer's Cut"") during sale on Steam saves some money.Some tips: Manual (dd_manual.pdf) and story (story.pdf) are inside the installed folder. 1 sub quest requires some reputation so always try to commit good deeds, there's no merit of committing bad ones. (You'll be arrested by guards or executed instantly!) Some skills make the game too easy, ""Aura of Command"" allows to manipulate all summoned creatures including enemy's, ""Deadly Gift"" allows to use ""Scorpion Trap"", which even tears the final boss apart.(Japanese translation below)==================================================ベルギーはLarianStudios製のDivinityシリーズ第1作を飾る、見下ろし視点の1人用ファンタジーRPG、日本語非対応なので語学力必須です。自由性が高く、いつ何処で何をするもプレイヤー次第、主人公は初期職業の種類に関係なく好きなスキルを自由に習得出来ます。ゲーム終盤は主人公が強くなりすぎたのか敵が弱すぎるのか多少退屈ですが、全体的な質は高く特にグラフィックとBGMは文句無しの出来栄え、膨大な数のサブクエストのおかげで最低40～60時間は遊べます。続編の完全版と番外編を含む3作のリマスター版が同梱されたアンソロジーをセール時に買うと少しだけ得します。プレイの上で役立つ情報：操作説明書とストーリー説明用のPDFファイルはインストール先のフォルダにあります、ファイル名はdd_manual.pdfとstory.pdfです。サブクエストの1つは名声値が必要なので出来るだけ善人プレイを心掛けましょう、このゲームで悪人プレイをする利点は皆無です。下手をすると衛兵に逮捕されるだけでは済まず現行犯でその場で処刑されます。召喚生物なら敵でも自分の手駒にできるAura of Commandと、最終ボスすら容易に引き裂く蠍の罠が使えるようになるDeadly Giftは、ゲームバランスを崩壊させる凶悪スキルです。"
76561198026316931,Recommended,214170,19813708,"Posted: 20 December, 2015",all,EolSunder,"A fun little RPG game of the Divinity series, not particular outstanding, but not one of the many boring rpgs out there. You can play as a few different types of characters, warrior, archer, mage, thief, but overall the warrior is vastly superior to the others, easier to play, easier to survive, and in the end he'll have tons of spells and thief abilities anyway. The first 2/3rds of the game is good, the last 1/3 is very rushed and weak so you'll get bored when you start doing the wasteland/ending parts of the game. Plus at that time you usually can kill most mobs in 2 hits so it isn't challenging when you start racking up 3000+ vitality and have all the super armor pieces you need to survive. Plus its pretty easy to cheat in the game with duping/etc so you have to limit yourself from not doing that. Overall, a nice basic rpg thats pretty long, you can get really cheap when its on sale, and will keep your attention for quite a while. A must buy for people who like rpgs, etc."
